attributes.review: I downloaded this app and IMMEDIATELY it’s asking for literally ALL of personal information (social security #, credit card #, the name and info of all my friends and ex-boyfriends) and kept on sending me AGGRESSIVE notifications, texts, and emails. This app won’t stop, and everything they’re sending is alarming and scary and frankly I am not comfortable with the contents inside the app either with extremely biased news and information leaning towards racist, white-supremeist, bigot ideals. Get it off this App Store before more people are subjected to this TORTURE of an app.
